13. Bg5 Be7 14. Bxf6 Bxf6 15. Kb1
{ Bida,M  (2212)  -Baratosi,D  (2424)  Baile Olanesti 2013 } 15... a5
{ Black may continue with ...a5-a4 and even ...Ra8-a5. Stockfish claims a small edge for White, but I think it's more smitten by White's typical space advantage than anything else. It's tough for White to create huge problems with the opposite color bishops in this semi-closed position. }
