6. a4
{ is a natural reaction to control b5, but the tradeoff is that White weakens b4. Black can exploit this with }
6... Nc6 { , when the knight is looking to settle on b4. } 7. d5 Nb4 8. Bg5 Bf5
{ Hitting c2. } 9. Bb3 c6 10. dxc6 Qxd1+ 11. Rxd1 bxc6 12. Rd2 e6 13. Nge2 Be7
