{ A novelty that GM Jones did not analyze back in 2010. Development remains Black's top priority! Kurajica played  14...Qf4  , but despite the inconvenience to White's king after  15.Rfd1  Qxh2+  16.Kf1  it was Black who turned out to be the victim of a vicious attack. }
15. Nb5 Qb6 16. Nxa7+ Kb8 17. Nb5 { Gaining the a-pawn has cost White time. }
